&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Prospecting, outbound calling, and responding to incoming inquiries from potential brokers&amp;nbsp;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Leading all communications with prospective brokers, including perfecting pitch calls, with the goal of turning leads into partners&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Collaborate with legal to perform background checks on prospective brokers, ensuring Splitero performs its proper due diligence&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Onboard all new brokers by developing, scheduling, and leading training&amp;nbsp;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Serve as the primary point of contact for all onboard brokers by answering questions, ensuring Splitero receives documentation for homeowners, and regularly reporting the status of opportunities&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Create processes and communication templates to be used by our production, focusing on providing an informative white-glove experience&amp;nbsp;&lt;/li&gt;
