&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;About the Job&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Splitero is seeking a results-oriented Vice President of Operations to lead our Underwriting, Processing, and Closing functions. In this role, you will be responsible for driving volume, operational performance, and company growth by developing high-performing teams, scalable processes, and a culture of accountability. You will translate business objectives into operational execution, develop strong managers, and continuously improve capacity, efficiency, and homeowner experience across the production funnel.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;As the leader of our production organization, you will leverage data, process improvement, and cross-functional collaboration to identify opportunities, remove operational bottlenecks, and enhance team performance. This role plays a critical part in scaling the business by increasing production capacity, improving operational effectiveness, and delivering exceptional experiences for both homeowners and employees.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Lead the Underwriting, Processing, and Closing functions to consistently drive revenue through achievement of origination, quality, velocity, and homeowner experience goals while ensuring operational excellence across the production funnel.&lt;/li&gt;
